			<h2>Correspondence</h2>
			<a class="xsmall link-alt" href="https://www.thesunmagazine.org/letter-to-the-editor">Write a Letter to the Editor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>
		</div>

		<div id="article-correspondences" class="correspondences correspondences-collapsed">
								<div class="block-correspondence" id="2925">
		<blockquote class="quote-2">
			<p>Alison Luterman&rsquo;s &ldquo;<a href="/article/1629">Leaving the Reservation</a>&rdquo; [June 1995] transfixed me. I could not bear it to end, and flipped ahead to see how much longer I had with her, for, as I read, I felt absolute recognition, joy, and admiration. I would have to stop now and then to look out at the soggy green field and the stubborn snow on the mountains beyond because I could not bear to let her story go by so fast.</p>
							<p class="quote-2-author">Grace Huffman<br>Woody Creek, Colorado</p>
					</blockquote>
	</div>

